<td class="mbox-text" style="">This article <b>needs <a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:Layout" title="Wikipedia:Layout">reorganization</a></b> to meet Wikipedia's <a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:Manual_of_Style" title="Wikipedia:Manual of Style">quality standards</a>. There is good information here, but it is poorly organized; editors are encouraged to <a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:Be_bold" title="Wikipedia:Be bold">be bold</a> and make changes to the overall structure to <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Pattern_language&amp;action=edit" class="external text" title="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Pattern_language&amp;action=edit" rel="nofollow">improve this article</a>. <small><i>(December 2006)</i></small></td>
